* Key-Value in-memory store with built-in persistence (snapshotting or journaling to disk)
** Emphasizes its powerful, optimized set of data structures and commands that allow
   users to simplify complex problems

Use cases include
* Storing user sessions
* Leaderboards
* Ordering by user votes
* Maintaining counts

